  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a small orb of lightning. By increasing the Chakra cost by 2, you can create additional orbs (up to 1 orb per 2 levels total). When performed, you can immediately fire any number of orbs you've created. The orbs have a Close range, and each orb can attack the same or a different creature, as you direct. An orb is a ranged attack that deals 1d6 electric damage.<br><br>If any orbs remain, they will circle you. As an attack action, you can fire any number of remaining orbs (as above). Alternatively, whenever you are hit by a natural weapon, unarmed attack or metal melee weapon, you can choose to have an orb meet the attack, shocking the attacker for 1d6 electric damage (this damage does not stack with that of Raidate no Jutsu).<br><br>Once used to attack or respond to an attack, an orb dissipates.</p>\n\n\n\n",
